    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's honestly such a gem! It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure with you! I\u2019ve priced it to move quickly, so come grab a bargain and let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
