    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced Double VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. While the finish shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are strong, offering the linear power delivery and tactile steering feedback that define this analog era of performance.",
