    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It drives beautifully and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with you today. I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
