    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen maintains its 8,400 RPM redline with precision, thanks to proactive rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis retains its Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functionality, providing a versatile range between compliance and track-ready stiffness. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and the interior displays slight bolster wear consistent with its mileage, the subframe and VANOS system have been inspected and remain in excellent operating condition. A true driver's car with the M Variable Differential providing exceptional mechanical grip.",
